div.div:
Refactor file handling to support UTF-16 encoding
- Updated CMakeUserPresets.json to change QML_DEBUG_ARGS and checksum. - Added new image files to the downloads directory. - Modified FileInfo.h to change string types to std::u16string for better Unicode support. - Updated FileInfoQtAdapter to accept std::u16string for file paths. - Changed SyncUploadQueue methods to accept std::u16string for file paths. - Enhanced logging to handle UTF-16 strings in log_headers.h and related files. - Refactored FileInfo.cpp to implement UTF-16 handling for file paths and names. - Updated FileListWidget and MainWindow to work with std::u16string. - Adjusted NotificationService to log file names in UTF-16. - Modified SyncUploadQueue and its private implementation to handle UTF-16 strings. - Added documentation for iconv conversions related to character encoding.
Refactor code structure and remove redundant changes
Created new branch master in hesphoros/CircularMenu

section.div: Account does not exists on github.community

Refactor UniConv header includes and add default encoding functionality
- Updated include directives in UniConv.h to use angle brackets for system headers. - Changed the path for the Singleton header to a more appropriate location. - Added a new method SetDefaultEncoding to the UniConv class to allow setting a default encoding. - Introduced a static member variable m_defaultEncoding to store the current encoding.
Add initial ScreenShot project files
- Created a new Visual Studio solution file for the ScreenShot project. - Added a project file for the ScreenShot application with configurations for Debug and Release modes. - Included filters for source files, header files, and resource files in the project. - Created a user-specific project file for storing user settings.
Implement ExtendedScreenshot functionality
- Developed the ExtendedScreenshot class to capture and edit screenshots. - Implemented various drawing tools including pen, rectangle, arrow, and text. - Added functionality for saving screenshots and copying to clipboard. - Created a user interface for selecting tools and colors during editing.
Enhance logging mechanism in LightLogWriteImpl
- Modified the log writing mechanism to check for a stop logging condition before pushing to the queue. - Updated the condition variable wait to include a check for bIsStopLogging to prevent blocking when logging is stopped.
